bio.title: About Me
bio.content:
Hello!

My name is Jackson Duke and I would like to thank you for taking the time to visit my website. I graduated from The University of Texas at Dallas with a BS in computer science on December 16, 2017.

I have experience in Java programming using the Spring framework, have done some previous digging into C#, familiar with Node.js and both the Angular and React frameworks.

If you would like to get in contact with me, please visit my LinedIn profile.
